arts%20of%20US%20work%20visa%20applications%20with%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20startup's%20immigrant%20founders%20say%20they%20experienced%20challenges%20navigating%20the%20US%20visa%20system.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGale's%20platform%20aims%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20process%20for%20applicants%20and%20free%20up%20lawyers'%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EGale%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20uses%20AI%20to%20streamline%20the%20US%20visa%20application%20process%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20employers%20and%20workers%2C%20has%20raised%20%242.7%20million%20in%20seed%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20cofounders%2C%20who%20are%20all%20immigrants%2C%20launched%20the%20startup%20out%20of%20Y%20Combinator's%202025%20winter%20cohort%20following%20their%20own%20frustrations%20navigating%20the%20US%20visa%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20%E2%80%94%20Rahul%20Gudise%2C%20Rishabh%20Sambare%2C%20and%20Haokun%20Qin%20%E2%80%94%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20found%20the%20process%20confusing%2C%20full%20of%20delays%2C%20and%20bureaucratic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20wanted%20a%20question%20answered%20about%20my%20visa%20status%2C%20it%20would%20take%20the%20attorneys%20like%20four%20business%20days%20to%20get%20back%20to%20me%2C%20minimum%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gudise%2C%20who%20previously%20worked%20at%20Tesla%20and%20Nvidia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20traditional%20approach%20of%20using%20law%20firms%20means%20cases%20can%20drag%20on%20for%20weeks%20unless%20clients%20are%20willing%20to%20pay%20premium%20fees.%20%26quot%3BSimple%20questions%20can%20take%20multiple%20steps%20to%20resolve%20because%20they%20have%20to%20be%20relayed%20up%20and%20down%20a%20chain%20of%20staff%20and%20attorneys%2C%26quot%3B%20Gudise%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGale's%20web-based%20platform%20automates%20much%20of%20the%20administrative%20work%20involved%20in%20visa%20applications.%20Instead%20of%20manually%20filling%20out%20lengthy%20forms%2C%20users%20can%20upload%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20passports%20for%20processing%20by%20the%20Gale%20platform.%20A%20licensed%20immigration%20lawyer%20conducts%20a%20final%20review%20before%20submission.%20Right%20now%2C%20the%20startup%20is%20focused%20on%20H-1B%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGudise%20said%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20onboarding%20%26quot%3Bas%20fast%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%20for%20applicants%2C%20and%20to%20free%20up%20time%20for%20lawyers%20by%20automating%20repetitive%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLawyers%20don't%20have%20to%20spend%20time%20on%20busywork%20or%20rely%20on%20paralegals%20for%20document%20prep%2C%26quot%3B%20Gudise%20said.%20The%20team%20aims%20to%20answer%20client%20questions%20within%20hours%2C%20rather%20than%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompliance%20is%20another%20key%20focus%20for%20Gale.%20Gudise%20said%20most%20law%20firms%20hand%20off%20the%20process%20once%20the%20visa%20is%20approved%2C%20leaving%20employers%20to%20handle%20ongoing%20requirements%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGale%20is%20building%20out%20its%20platform%20to%20monitor%20changes%20like%20job%20titles%20or%20promotions%20that%20might%20impact%20a%20worker's%20visa%20status.%20The%20team%20is%20also%20developing%20integrations%20with%20company%20HR%20systems%20to%20help%20employers%20stay%20compliant%20as%20requirements%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGale%20plans%20to%20use%20the%20new%20funding%20to%20boost%20its%20compliance%20tools%20and%20grow%20the%20team.%20Building%20new%20partnerships%20with%20employers%20and%20immigration%20lawyers%20is%20also%20a%20key%20focus%20as%20the%20company%20scales%2C%20Qin%20told%20BI.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20we%20want%20to%20promote%20legal%20immigration%20to%20the%20States%20and%20help%20employers%20stay%20compliant.%20This%20is%20the%20way%20to%20do%20it%20sustainably%2C%26quot%3B%20Gudise%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup's%20seed%20round%20was%20led%20by%20Axiom%20Partners%2C%20with%20participation%20f