%20Masters%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6838ab93ca50259add4d4e32%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERory%20McIlroy%20won%20the%202025%20Masters%20tournament%20after%20blowing%20a%20big%20lead.%3Cp%3ERichard%20Heathcote%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETiger%20Global%20told%20investors%20in%20a%20recent%20letter%20that%20the%20firm%20is%20%26quot%3Bintently%20focused%20on%20playing%20our%20game.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20%2450%20billion%20manager%20put%20in%20new%20%26quot%3Benhanced%20risk%20management%20processes%26quot%3B%20since%20its%2056%25%20loss%20in%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20letter%20ended%20with%20a%20comparison%20between%20the%20firm's%20resurgence%20and%20golfer%20Rory%20McIlroy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Tiger%20Global%20nears%20its%2025th%20anniversary%2C%20the%20New%20York-based%20stockpicker%20is%20ready%20to%20move%20on%20from%20its%20recent%20past%20and%20return%20to%20its%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2450%20billion%20manager%2C%20founded%20and%20run%20by%20billionaire%20Chase%20Coleman%2C%20posted%20back-to-back%20annual%20losses%20in%202021%20and%202022%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20being%20a%2056%25%20swoon%20that%20brought%20about%20%26quot%3Benhanced%20risk%20management%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20firm's%20investment%20team%20told%20investors%20in%20an%20April%20letter%20seen%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20since%20then%3A%20A%20two-year%20resurgence%20for%20one%20of%20the%20original%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-julian-robertsons-tiger-network-spans-hundreds-of-funds-2019-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETiger%20Cubs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20gains%20of%2028.5%25%20and%2024%25%20in%202023%20and%202024%2C%20respectively.%20The%20letter%20notes%20the%20firm%20was%20up%202.5%25%20in%20its%20hedge%20fund%20in%202025's%20volatile%20first%20quarter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRegular%20reviews%20of%20market%20and%20macro%20variables%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20stress%20tests%20of%20each%20holding%2C%20have%20helped%20the%20firm%20get%20back%20on%20track%20and%20lets%20the%20investment%20team%20be%20%26quot%3Bintently%20focused%20on%20playing%20our%20game%20%E2%80%94%20relying%20on%20the%20fundamental%20research%20process%20we%20have%20refined%20over%20decades%2C%20visualizing%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20outcomes%2C%20and%20prioritizing%20resilience%20across%20the%20companies%20we%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20notes%20that%20the%20investment%20team%20has%20%26quot%3Bstepped%20up%20the%20cadence%20of%20internal%20communication%26quot%3B%20and%20become%20%26quot%3Bavid%20users%26quot%3B%20of%20OpenAI's%20Deep%20Research%20agent.%20Tiger%20Global%20is%20an%20investor%20in%20the%20AI%20pioneer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20compared%20its%20response%20to%20its%20poor%20stretch%20to%20the%20perseverance%20of%20pro%20golfer%20Rory%20McIlroy%2C%20the%20winner%20of%20this%20year's%20Masters%20tournament.%20McIlroy%20nearly%20blew%20a%20big%20lead%20before%20rallying%20to%20win%20in%20a%20do-or-die%20scenario%20after%20a%20lighthearted%20pep%20talk%20from%20his%20caddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20Rory%2C%20we%20expect%20to%20make%20some%20double%20bogeys%20as%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20Tiger's%20team%20said%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20missteps%20and%20losses%20are%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20%26quot%3BBut%20by%20relying%20on%20our%20research%20process%20and%20approaching%20every%20day%20with%20resilience%20and%20a%20prepared%20mind%2C%20we%20know%20we%20will%20make%20many%20more%20birdies%20and%20eagles%20over%20time%20and%20hopefully%20win%20some%20more%20championships%20along%20the%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20%26quot%3Bbattle-tested%26quot%3B%20investment%20approach%2C%20the%20firm%20told%20LPs%20its%20process%20can%20handle%20the%20chopp