%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-28T091611.656_11zon-1748403985-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-28T091611.656_11zon-1748403985-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440072%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESushmita%20travelled%20across%20India%20to%20learn%20about%20all%20the%20art%20forms%20that%20are%20becoming%20endangered%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F278803%2Fias-hero-uplifts-jharkhand-sabar-tribes-from-poverty%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartisans%20were%20disheartened%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20feeling%20that%20their%20hard%20work%20was%20neither%20recognised%20nor%20fairly%20valued.%20When%20I%20spoke%20to%20one%20of%20them%20and%20asked%20whether%20he%20would%20encourage%20his%20son%20to%20carry%20on%20the%20tradition%2C%20he%20grew%20visibly%20angry.%20He%20told%20me%20he%20would%20advise%20his%20son%20to%20find%20a%20regular%20job%20instead.%20That%20moment%20was%20a%20turning%20point%20for%20me%2C%20and%20I%20realised%20we%20needed%20to%20preserve%20these%20traditional%20crafts%20and%20empower%20the%20artisans%20to%20earn%20a%20sustainable%20livelihood.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoved%20by%20the%20struggles%20of%20the%20Nirmal%20artisans%20and%20after%20spending%20another%20year%20travelling%20across%20the%20country%20to%20connect%20with%20other%20craftsmen%2C%20Sushmita%20founded%20%E2%80%98Gullakaari%E2%80%99%20in%20April%202023.%20The%20platform%20is%20designed%20to%20connect%20artisans%20with%20customers%2C%20co-create%20art%2C%20and%20raise%20awareness%20about%20endangered%20art%20forms%20while%20helping%20artisans%20sustain%20their%20livelihoods.%20The%20vision%20behind%20Gullakaari%20is%20to%20give%20traditional%20art%20the%20respect%20and%20recognition%20it%20deserves.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20organisation%E2%80%99s%20mission%20is%20to%20preserve%20India%E2%80%99s%20cultural%20heritage%20while%20making%20these%20crafts%20relevant%20to%20modern%20consumers.%20By%20offering%20a%20marketplace%20for%20traditional%20art%20forms%20like%20Warli%2C%20Patachitra%2C%20Gond%2C%20and%20Tholu%20Bommalata%2C%20the%20platform%20allows%20artisans%20to%20reach%20a%20broader%20audience%20and%20benefit%20from%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20orders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20ancient%20art%20meets%20AR%20and%20QR%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20people%20ask%20the%20social%20entrepreneur%20where%20she%20has%20used%20her%20software%20engineering%20skills%20in%20her%20work%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20use%20tech%20only%20where%20it%20adds%20value%20without%20altering%20the%20soul%20of%20the%20craft.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20trained%20the%20Tholu%20Bommalata%20artisans%20to%20create%20lampshades%2C%20incorporating%203D-printed%20logos%20for%20corporate%20clients.%20The%20traditional%20leather%20puppetry%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20once%20a%20vibrant%20form%20of%20storytelling%2C%20but%20now%2C%20it%20has%20nearly%20vanished.%20We%20have%20used%20technology%20in%20a%20way%20that%20when%20it%20is%20lit%2C%20the%20lamp%20beautifully%20illuminates%20not%20only%20the%20intricate%20art%20but%20also%20a%203D-printed%20logo%2C%20blending%20heritage%20with%20modern%20technology.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-me