200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-28T092821.995_11zon-1748404801.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sushmita's%20parents%20always%20supported%20her%20through%20this%20journey%20of%20becoming%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-28T092821.995_11zon-1748404801.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-28T092821.995_11zon-1748404801-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-28T092821.995_11zon-1748404801-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-28T092821.995_11zon-1748404801-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-05-28T092821.995_11zon-1748404801-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440091%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESushmita%E2%80%99s%20parents%20always%20supported%20her%20through%20this%20journey%20of%20becoming%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20asked%20about%20the%20sales%20and%20overall%20profits%2C%20the%20social%20entrepreneur%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CAt%20present%2C%20our%20primary%20buyers%20are%20corporates%2C%20and%20we%20are%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F426169%2Frescript-naren-raj-ashutosh-ananth-recycling-waste-paper-sustainab