icularly%20in%20how%20she's%20turned%20skincare%20routines%20into%20viral%20content%20pieces%20that%20move%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bglazed%20donut%26quot%3B%20trend%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20has%20since%20inspired%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnail-manicure-trends-popular-and-out-now-winter-nail-techs-2024-11%23glazed-doughnut-nails-still-take-the-cake-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bglazed%20donut%20nails%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20TikTok%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ferewhon-sells-40-000-hailey-biebers-strawberry-skin-glaze-smoothies-a-month-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eviral%20%2420%20Strawberry%20Skin%20Glaze%20smoothie%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Erewhon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e85b4387-90d3-4736-8ea0-8840e67eb54a%5C%22%3ENot%20trying%20to%20be%20everything%20to%20everyone%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20packaging%20matters%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScott%20said%20Rhode's%20brand%20language%20of%20minimalist%20packaging%2C%20soft%20lighting%2C%20and%20the%20dewy%20%26quot%3Bglazed%20donut%26quot%3B%20look%20reinforces%20Rhode's%20identity%20and%20sets%20it%20apart%20from%20more%20maximalist%2C%20or%20color-focused%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERhode%20sells%20only%2010%20products%2C%20the%20bulk%20of%20which%20are%20skincare-focused.%20These%20include%20a%20cleanser%2C%20lip%20balms%2C%20blush%2C%20moisturizer%2C%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20product%20packaging%20is%20as%20restrained%20as%20the%20product%20selection%2C%20with%20neutral%20grays%2C%20beiges%2C%20and%20browns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20minimalism%2C%20paired%20with%20affordable%20pricing%20and%20ingredient%20transparency%2C%20directly%20tapped%20into%20the%20'skinimalism'%20and%20'Clean%20Girl'%20trends%20popular%20with%20Gen%20Z%20and%20young%20millennials%2C%26quot%3B%20Scott%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETeng%20Chan%20Leong%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Skribble%2C%20a%20Malaysia-b