on%20high-quality%2C%20beautifully%20designed%20planters%20and%20seats%20made%20from%20virgin%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20Sereno%20won%20the%20CIA%20Design%20Excellence%20Award%2C%20a%20prestigious%20recognition%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Interior%20Designers%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20Japan.%20The%20company%20also%20picked%20up%20three%20European%20design%20awards%2C%20a%20sure%20sign%20of%20its%20strong%20design%20ethos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20virgin%20plastic%20to%20repurposed%20waste%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20years%2C%20sustainability%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20the%20priority.%20%E2%80%9CPlastic%20was%20the%20mode%20of%20manufacturing%20in%202013%2C%E2%80%9D%20Yuvraj%20explains.%20But%20the%20shift%20came%20gradually.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsereno.co.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBy%202018%2C%20Sereno%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20tapping%20into%20its%20own%20factory%20waste%2C%20trimmings%2C%20and%20rejections%2C%20which%20used%20to%20end%20up%20unused%2C%20to%20make%20planters%2C%20aligning%20more%20closely%20with%20the%20principles%20of%20reuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20pivot%20came%20post-COVID%2C%20in%202021%2C%20under%20pressure%20from%20European%20buyers%20to%20look%20beyond%20internal%20waste%20and%20explore%20broader%20sustainability.%20Initially%20sceptical%2C%20especially%20about%20the%20quality%20of%20externally%20sourced%20plastics%2C%20Yuvraj%20began%20investigating%20global%20models.%20%E2%80%9CEurope%20was%20collecting%20fishing%20nets%20and%20plastic%20debris%20from%20the%20ocean.%20While%20I%20liked%20that%20idea%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20an%20effective%20solution%20that%20would%20solve%20something%20in%20India%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20circular%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20Sereno%20began%20experimenting%20with%20post-consumer%20waste%3A%20milk%20bags%2C%20shampoo%20bottles%2C%20and%20single-use%20plastics%2C%20before%20they%20could%20reach%20landfills.%20The%20team%20cracked%20a%20formula%20that%20allowed%20them%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F397387%2Fbihar-brothers-transform-plastic-waste-into-stunning-eco-friendly-furniture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretain%20durability%20and%20aesthetics%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20using%20repurposed%20plastic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22recycling%20process%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-05-28T175743.611-1748435300-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440447%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-elem