block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20to%20seek%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20emotional%20challenges%20of%20the%20postpartum%20period%20last%20beyond%20two%20weeks%2C%20it%20may%20point%20to%20Postpartum%20Depression%20(PPD)%2C%20which%20can%20bring%20intense%20mood%20changes%2C%20frequent%20crying%2C%20or%20feelings%20of%20being%20overwhelmed.%20In%20rare%20cases%2C%20some%20mothers%20may%20experience%20more%20severe%20symptoms%2C%20known%20as%20Postpartum%20Psychosis%2C%20which%20can%20include%20confusion%2C%20unusual%20thoughts%2C%20or%20strong%20emotional%20distress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20conditions%20are%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331532%2Ftherapy-in-chennai-mental-health-cafe-wellness-centre-pooja-srinivasa-love-hope-company%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20treatable%20with%20the%20right%20care%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Harish.%20%E2%80%9CWith%20support%20from%20loved%20ones%2C%20regular%20follow-ups%2C%20and%20professional%20guidance%20%E2%80%94%20often%20a%20mix%20of%20counselling%20and%20medication%20%E2%80%94%20recovery%20is%20very%20much%20possible.%20In%20most%20cases%20I%E2%80%99ve%20seen%2C%20mothers%20began%20to%20feel%20better%20within%20two%20to%20three%20weeks.%20Even%20when%20hospitalisation%20was%20needed%2C%20one%20mother%20recovered%20steadily%20within%2010%20days.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20right%20care%2C%20postpartum%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20be%20a%20story%20of%20struggle.%20As%20Sharanya%20and%20Aminta%20show%2C%20it%20can%20also%20be%20a%20journey%20of%20healing%2C%20strength%2C%20and%20rediscovery%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20when%20women%20are%20not%20left%20to%20do%20it%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748441400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%22%2C