ng%20for%20someone%20with%20schizophrenia.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Shaji%20also%20highlights%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F436999%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-day-films-india-sensitive-portrayals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommon%20misconceptions%20%3C%2Fa%3Esurrounding%20schizophrenia%2C%20particularly%20the%20belief%20that%20people%20with%20the%20condition%20are%20violent%20or%20possessed.%20He%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CLess%20than%20five%20percent%20of%20people%20with%20schizophrenia%20are%20violent.%20There%20is%20more%20violence%20in%20the%20general%20population.%E2%80%9D%20Yet%20stigma%20remains.%20Many%20families%20still%20approach%20religious%20figures%2C%20assuming%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20work%20of%20evil%20spirits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMental%20health%20disorders%20and%20caregiver%20struggles%20need%20to%20be%20normalised%20so%20that%20a%20wider%20and%20stronger%20support%20system%20can%20be%20put%20in%20place%20%E2%80%94%20for%20both%20those%20battling%20the%20disease%20and%20those%20caring%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahira%20insists.%20%E2%80%9COrganisations%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F436999%2Fschizophrenia-awareness-day-films-india-sensitive-portrayals%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmaha%20Health%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20already%20actively%20building%20mental%20health%20support%20ecosystems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Caregiving%20had%20seeped%20into%20every%20part%20of%20my%20life%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMahira%20was%20so%20consumed%20by%20caring%20for%20Naina%20that%20her%20illness%20gradually%20became%20the%20central%20theme%20of%20her%20life.%20It%20shaped%20not%20only%20how%20she%20spent%20her%20days%20but%20also%20how%20she%20saw%20herself.%20The%20experience%20ran%20so%20deep%20that%20Mahira%20even%20chose%20to%20pursue%20psychology%20professionally%2C%20hoping%20to%20better%20understand%20what%20her%20family%20was%20going%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20delving%20deeper%20into%20the%20field%20with%20a%20few%20degrees%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20my%20experiences%20with%20mental%20illness%20all%20my%20life%20made%20it%20hard%20for%20me%20to%20stay%20objective%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20realisation%20made%20her%20reflect%20on%20how%20caregiving%20had%20silently%20spread%20into%20every%20corner%20of%20her%20identity.%20%E2%80%9CCaregiving%20had%20seeped%20into%20every%20part%20of%20my%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mahira%20reflects.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20problem%20solver%20at%20heart%2C%20I%20would%20always%20leap%20into%20survival%20mode%20before%20even%20acknowledging%20how%20I%20felt%20in%20the%20moment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-53_11zon-1748415895.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caring%20for%20Naina%20reshaped%20Mahira%E2%80%99s%20identity%20and%20led%20her%20to%20study%20psychology.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-53_11zon-1748415895.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-53_11zon-1748415895-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-53_11zon-1748415895-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-53_11zon-1748415895-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-53_11zon-1748415895-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440219%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECaring%20for%20Naina%20reshaped%20Mahira%E2%80%99s%20identity%20and%20led%20her%20to%20study%20psychology.%20Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20that%20constant%20state%20of%20alertness%20began%20to%20take%20its%20toll.%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20being%20an%20adult%20too%20early%20in%20life%2C%20I%20once%20believed%20that%20I%20never%20wanted%20a%20family%2C%20fearing%20the%20load%20of%20responsibilities%20it%20comes%20with%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSomewhere%20along%20the%20way%2C%20I%20learnt%20to%20be%20the%20adult%20in%20every%20room%2C%20to%20fix%20things%20before%20anyone%20asked.%20And%20when%20you%E2%80%99re%20always%20solving%20other%20people%E2%80%99s%20problems%2C%20you%20stop%20letting%20yourself%20feel%20your%20own.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20scared%20me%20most%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20having%20a%20family%20%E2%80%94%20what%20if%20I%20disappeared%20into%20it%20too%3F%20And%20more%20importantly%2C%20what%20if%20I%20was%20just%20too%20burnt%20out%20to%20do%20it%20justice%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Choosing%20myself%20was%20tough%2C%20but%20important%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELife%20had%20other%20plans%20for%20her%2C%20and%20her%20husband%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20her%20biggest%20support%20system.%20With%20that%20new%20foundation%20in%20place%2C%20Mahira%20began%20to%20rediscover%20herself.%20When%20Naina%20relapsed%20years%20later%2C%20Mahira%20was%20struggling%20with%20her%20own%20mental%20health%20and%20had%20a%20new%20family%20to%20care%20for%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20sister%20a