C%20school%20counsellors%20should%20be%20well%20trained%20and%20alert%20to%20early%20warning%20signs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-54_11zon-1748416077.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22There%20is%20a%20dire%20need%20for%20public%20forums%20or%20active%20communities%20for%20caregivers%20to%20turn%20to.%20Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-54_11zon-1748416077.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-54_11zon-1748416077-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-54_11zon-1748416077-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-54_11zon-1748416077-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Ffeatured-img-54_11zon-1748416077-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-440222%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20a%20dire%20need%20for%20public%20forums%20or%20active%20communities%20for%20caregivers%20to%20turn%20to.%20Representational%20picture%20source%3A%20Shutterstock.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20legal%20system%20in%20India%20also%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20nuanced.%20Some%20laws%20designed%20to%20protect%20the%20patients%20could%20backfire%20and%20hinder%20treatment%20because%20of%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20mental%20illnesses.%20For%20instance%2C%20a%20person%20can%20be%20admitted%20to%20a%20psychiatric%20facility%20only%20with%20their%20consent.%20But%20when%20mental%20illness%20plays%20with%20a%20person%E2%80